Quote: Miss Newlands never owned a strap, but successfully wielded something far more satisfactory - a supple-jack. A pupil would be sent over the back fence into the bush to cut suitable lengths of this native vine that, as its name implies, is very pliable and can inflect [sic] a stinging lash.
